ly explain differences between dense-bound and diffuse-open star\nclusters. We also predict, as a consequence of feedback, a $4-6$ Myr age\ndifference for massive clusters with multiple generations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Apr 2017 18:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Jul 2017 13:44:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-25"}
